cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a novel visual tracking method that involves image processing and computer vision techniques. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new similarity metric and an online template updating strategy, both of which involve machine learning concepts. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the proposed method involves intelligent decision-making for target tracking. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with visual tracking in multimedia data. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the proposed method can be applied to robotic vision for tracking objects.
